comment: Graveyard: activates after killing Doctor Ickus

NECROLORDS: AoE Damage Proc Aura -

Using  Fleshcraft on the Gushing Slime's corpse will grant the Corrosive Gunk aura for 3 minutes.

This aura will apply the  Corrosive Gunk buff to any nearby party member, giving a 10% chance to proc AoE damage around your character!

NECROLORD: 25% Damage Reduction Aura - 
Using  Fleshcraft on the Congealed Slime's corpse will grant the Congealed Contagion aura for 3 minutes.

This aura will apply the  Congealed Contagion buff to any nearby party member within 10 yards, giving them with 25% Damage Reduction!

NECROLORDS: 25% Haste Aura -  
Using  Fleshcraft on the Pestilence Slime's corpse will grant the   Rapid Infection aura for 3 minutes.

This aura will apply the  Rapid Infection buff to any nearby party member within 10 yards, providing them with 25% Haste!
